===================
INTRODUCTION
===================

BASE REQUIREMENTS:
   PostNuke Web Portal System
   http://www.postnuke.com

IN THE W3C HTML VALIDATOR:
   Valid HTML 4.01 Transitional
   Valid CSS 2
   
TESTED WITH THE FOLLOWING SOFTWARES:
   Linux RH7.1
   MyDowz 2000
   PHP 4.06 (http://www.php.net)
   PostNuke 0.62 (http://www.postnuke.com)
   Opera 5.x
   Mozilla 0.9.3 (http://www.mozilla.org)
   Konqueror
   Netscape 4.x & N6
   Internet Explorer 5.x
    
===================
INSTALLATION
===================
     
   Untar/unzip to a temp folder
   Copy the evolution Folder into your PostNuke Themes folder => http://www.Your-Url/themes/   
   You' re done


===================
TROUBLESHOOTING ???
===================

Read our FAQ, Look at the forums, perhaps the solution is here :)
http://www.PostNuke.com
     
===================
FINAL NOTES
===================

I hope you' ll enjoy evolution.
Have Fun!

